    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about keeping it spotless and garage-kept. You really won't find a scratch on it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
