    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its factory-spec performance. The high-revving S54 power plant remains pristine, featuring a fully serviced double-VANOS system and rod bearing replacement for long-term reliability. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement, eliminating common structural fatigue points. Suspension dynamics are factory-fresh, retaining the original geometry and damping characteristics that define this longitudinal, rear-wheel-drive icon. No fluid seepage, no bushing play\u2014just pure mechanical harmony.",
